{
  "id": "RAW_aa9f57",
  "title": "即梦图片 4.0 上线 4K 直出，这就是 AI 人像的新巅峰。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647675217&idx=1&sn=9337791fdad7bf4d8686d3e812305988",
  "date": "2025-09-19 01:31:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">起猛了，即梦上线4K直出了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，免费。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191528\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6768518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=beeca438&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nbXTS2NviblgaYRrOvLn6OBQDIY2NM2iaHWQUv5C9b17d9my7pZZ4R6rQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我在上周，就写过一篇即梦4.0的玩法：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647674914&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4fc65cb53503b1d8453b55c929da4fd5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"即梦图片4.0来了，我整理了10个好用到爆的进阶玩法。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">即梦图片4.0来了，我整理了10个好用到爆的进阶玩法。</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在当时，即梦只支持2K分辨率，并不支持4K的分辨率直出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">注意我说的是直出，不是你生成个2K的图然后用即梦超分到4K，是模型原生直出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而现在，支持了，而且，免费。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191529\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44537037037037036\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37350fe2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74n4mxw3rcTevxp1jKgia8Mno9ISeBJIPIwEDic23XL90ic8jzibknI1mkojg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我第一时间测试后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我真的想说，这，就是AI人像的，新巅峰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前2K虽然在做人物半身和特写之类的很强，但是还是一直有个问题，就是一旦是中景，人物的脸几乎都不太行，特别是眼睛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我用文字表达可能很难理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我放一波2K的@染夏的AI模特图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191530\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3fc5c23&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nYaK8m350wRMia0whNRibTRoRmvicTmA0lMiaFuIh3DMScNgxW28xKWFd0Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可能已经有部分眼尖的朋友，感受到图里很不舒服的点了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我给大家截一下大图看看，做好心理准备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191532\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6277777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=451c129f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nBIEVrCyTUNrH4c4mvG2drgiaaSQLusXicXJTr196uUQ11gw3Ln1XWN7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191531\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5461200585651538\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3d6703b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nicJeiacZ3ib7tBaGHkoBqnu1y0WY5fHmcLZusnNNjc4kf6iaCyGoKXgib9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">眼睛，从来都是心灵的窗户，我们对眼睛也非常的敏感，在2K这种尺度下，因为是中景，分配给脸部的像素本来就不多，而给眼睛的就更少了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，有的时候，就经常会因为眼睛的崩盘，而让整个图片，显得非常像伪人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让本来好好的AI模特摄影图，呈现出一个完全不可用的状态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而现在，即梦图片4.0 4K的上线，则，完美的解决了这个问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不仅整体输出的光影更完美、细节质感更强，人脸的变形也几乎被解决了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还是我的这个AI模特@染夏来举例子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191533\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fdf2fd80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nygGyPDMqwUNMGdeeJ2fhguDH1tNClQyKWs0eSjuBZtAWPn0iaYE20uA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们现在在基于这个图，给她一个Prompt：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">保持原图模特，生成新的图片。全景照片，人像摄影，一张充满异域风情和建筑美感的照片，一个女生斜靠在摩洛哥传统庭院（Riad）的回廊立柱上。午后的阳光穿过庭院顶棚和雕花繁复的木质窗格（Mashrabiya），在马赛克瓷砖地面和她身上投下复杂的、充满韵律感的几何形光影图案。整个环境色彩浓郁，光影就是最好的装饰。她穿着一件素色的长袍。生成同一模特和服饰下，不同角度、不同动作、不同表情的系列图片。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让我们来看看，4K直出的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191539\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df3cf5e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nthIfOPsRqkWljhAWjCKWhxUR0np0uPMqfAAofANZVhSe3q95l1nkeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191535\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4c94629&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74n4IAZUszphtfxCmbzUyicsD2XsWFXQ5v1ib1ibxYuibeiccHgSniaFbrmbwaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191536\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1aed2fd2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74n7IydFJrSniasr3jWCJicuxicdMdK5lqaoXEacibT9VJGOnWRaHyr7eOZzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191538\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a5e4a6c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74ncib2Vjxnxc1kWBnLHkiaGSwpgQ0sKrmMfbLwfnFAyjVXycbr19we6kiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我的文章里，很少用很大的版面来展示图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是这篇文章，我贪心了一点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为在我的审美里，这真的很美，我也很想分享给你们看看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从2K到4K，真的不仅仅是参数的提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它是一道那种，越过了临界点的坎，一道从像到是的坎。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2K的模型，给我的感觉，就像一个技艺高超但总是差一口气的画师。他能画出完美的骨相、皮肤的质感、衣服的褶皱，但在最关键的地方，也就是眼睛，他会露怯。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那双眼睛里，你看不到故事，看不到情绪，只有一种空洞的属于算法的正确。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而4K，就是画龙点睛的最后一步。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当分辨率的暴力，足以支撑模型在几毫米的眼眶里，去描绘瞳孔的光泽、睫毛的投影、眼神里那一丝若有若无的情绪时，这个AI生成的人，我觉得，就真正活了过来。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;display:inline !important;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;float:none;text-transfor