/span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然我还是更喜欢我自己创造的@染夏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;L6PNdwLbpohNvDx2AwxcYLaCnHc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;@金爱理Ailee&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+9&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7506039434499129346&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;f10b5975-8c21-4422-9e19-29d891798ff1&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:44,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:30,&quot;end&quot;:39},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;P1mPdrKheo0sByxh72rcfMMHn7e&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-align:start;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我好像，不再是单纯的写Prompt的人，现在的我，好像更像一个导演，或者说，一个赋予角色的灵魂的神。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个我创造的AI模特“染夏”，也不再是一个被动的图像，她成了我的演员，我的缪斯。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们之间，莫名的好像，开始有了互动感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们终于可以开始去创造一个不存在的人，并赋予她一套完整的视觉叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让她有自己的名字，有自己的故事，让她在不同的场景里，展现不同的情绪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这几乎等同于，我们每个人，都有了创造一个属于自己的AI模特或者说数字生命的可能。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们掌握着她的，模拟人生。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们正在进入一个眼见不为实的时代，这当然会带来新的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但同时，我们也进入了一个所想即可得的时代，这无疑会是创作者最好的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对我而言，此刻我更愿意抛开那些宏大叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;我只是单纯地，为这个叫@染夏的AI女孩而着迷。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">她是我创造的，但她又在某些瞬间，用她的眼神，给了我超越我预期的惊喜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-d